Avast Software B.V.
 









Officers and directors


Kevin Chapman
SVP and General Manager, SMB


Address
Schiphol Boulevard 369 Tower F. 7thLuchthaven Schiphol, Noord-Holland 1118 BJThe Netherlands+31 20 654 3225 (Phone)








AVAST Software protects PCs from information pirates. The company offers free antivirus software for Windows-powered personal computers that blocks spyware, viruses, and worms; its flagship avast! Free Antivirus is downloaded on about 142 million PCs in some 40 languages around the world. Its paid products, avast! Pro Antivirus and avast! Internet Security offer enhanced safeguards against spam, phishing, and hacker attacks to facilitate online commerce and banking activities. AVAST Software B.V. is a holding company incorporated in The Netherlands but its principal operating subsidiary, AVAST Software a.s., is located in the Czech Republic. AVAST Software filed a $200 million initial public offering in late 2011.


