                        Why do I need anti-malware software?                      


The internet is arguably the most powerful tool out there for education, commerce, and connecting the whole world. However, the internet is also a very dark and dangerous place. The internet is infested with software that is specifically designed to disrupt, damage, and obtain unauthorized access to your computer system. Also known as Malware. Malware comes in so many different shapes and sizes. It is practically impossible to say how many different types of malware there is because new types are being developed every single day. Anti-malware software is something you should seriously consider looking into.
